Story
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey who resided on a jamoon(berry) tree which was on the banks of the river. In the same forest,
there lived a crocodile and his wife. One day crocodile came to banks of the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted monkey offered 
him some berries. The crocodile came back for more berries as he liked them. As days passed, the crocodile and monkey became good friends.